  20: 34 address, constant, overlay - address can be reused as constant; code/data overlay allowed
  21: 4A exec, display-byte - display byte role allowed
  22: 01 exec, display-byte - display byte role allowed
  23: 04 exec, display-byte - display byte role allowed"
`;

