  __loop_0: 00
  __if_false_1: 06
  __spatial_hit_mines: 64

Optimizations:
  - intent-domain-lowering: Lowered 3 state fields and 2 rules through the generic intent pipeline.
  - auto-preload-initial-state: Moved initial state into setup/preload values so official program cells stay focused on turn logic.
  - intent-read-lowering: Lowered read at line 24 to calculator stop plus register store.
  - spatial-hit-condition-helper: Tested bit_has() through the shared spatial hit helper at line 26.
  - error-stop: Used one-cell error opcode for literal ЕГГ0Г stop at line 20.
  - single-use-rule-inline: Inlined single-use rule exploded at line 27.
  - spatial-neighbor-count-unroll: Lowered neighbor_count(mines, ...) as 8 register-accumulated spatial hits.
  - display-strategy-selection: Selected decimal-pack for screen __inline_show_39_0.
  - display-current-x-reuse: Reused clue already in X as the first field of screen __inline_show_39_0.
  - packed-display-lowering: Display __inline_show_39_0 may use display-byte encodings in later layout passes.
  - single-use-rule-inline: Inlined single-use rule reveal_safe_cell at line 30.
  - terminal-branch-end-elision: Omitted unreachable if-end jump after terminal then branch at line 26.
  - bit-mask-quotient-reuse: Reused __spatial_hit_mines / 4 through __spatial_hit_mines while building bit_mask().
  - store-recall-peephole: Dropped 3 redundant П->X immediately after X->П to the same register.
  - dead-store-elimination: Removed 2 store(s) to register(s) never read before the next assignment.
  - constant-folding: Dropped 1 identity arithmetic operation(s) (0+ or 1*).
  - preloaded-indirect-flow: Activated post-layout: replaced 10 direct branch/call(s) with proven preloaded indirect flow.
  - dark-entry-layout: Pointed 1 branch(es) at an executable suffix through a proven dark-entry formal address (beyond the 104-cell window).
  - generated-setup-program: Generated optimized setup program for mines.
  - setup-int-random-range-lowering: Lowered int(random() * 999) without К [x] so the MK-61 random sequence keeps moving.

Candidates:
  * display __inline_show_39_0/decimal-pack: 1 steps; selected decimal-pack for screen __inline_show_39_0
  - display __inline_show_39_0/packed-storage-reuse: 999999 steps; display fields are not proved to already occupy their decimal positions
  - display __inline_show_39_0/packed-display-helper: 2 steps; display is not repeated often enough for a shared packed display helper
  - display __inline_show_39_0/display-byte-helper: 999999 steps; display is not repeated often enough for a shared display-byte helper
  - display __inline_show_39_0/display-byte-builder: 999999 steps; display has no literal/X2-sensitive fragments to build
  * ir-pass/preloaded-indirect-flow: 1 steps; compiler-owned address preload selected for one-cell indirect branch/call

Optimizer Capabilities:
  - store-recall-peephole: active; Elides immediate X->П r / П->X r pairs when no exact-machine effect is crossed.
  - stack-current-x-scheduling: candidate; Keeps a just-computed value in X for a following commutative use and removes the temporary store after data-flow proof.
  - tail-call-lowering: active; Replaces subroutine calls in tail position with direct jumps so rule factoring and terminal branches do not force extra returns or branch hops.
  - return-zero-jump: candidate; Uses В/О as one-cell БП 01 only when the return stack is known empty.
  - vo-return-body-reorder: candidate; Candidate: reorder HEAD/MAIN/SUB so a subroutine return lands at the program head and a ПП/В/О pair collapses. Single-use procedures are already inlined and tail-position calls already become direct jumps, so the remaining gain needs a global layout search with no proven safe trigger on the current programs.
  - super-number-deferred-normalization: candidate; Candidate: keep an un-normalized super-number (extra hidden mantissa digits) to defer a range/error check. The reference emulator models only the 8 visible mantissa digits, so the hidden-digit behavior the idiom relies on cannot be reproduced or safely proven, and no language construct produces it.
  - packed-position-type: candidate; Candidate: a language-level packed position type N.0000H carrying an integer position plus packed (hex) fractional sub-coordinates. The dual-use round-trip (К [x] recovers the position, К {x} recovers the packed fraction) is already exploited by constants-dual-use; a dedicated type would only add language surface that no current program consumes.
  - coord-list-scaled-decimal: candidate; Stores 10x10 board coordinates as y.x decimal values when all visible uses allow it, so row/column/diagonal scans avoid repeated /10 digit extraction.
  - dual-constant-sign-digit: candidate; Candidate: a language intent for a dual constant 1.|-00 plus compact sign-digits (2N..9N) and their comparison semantics. The negative-zero comparison behavior is already active through the negative-zero-threshold family; no current program needs the additional sign-digit literal surface.
  - branch-removal: candidate; Umbrella rule for replacing provably equivalent conditionals with branchless arithmetic, sign, extrema, or masked updates.
  - zero-condition-test: active; Uses direct F x?0 tests when one side of a condition is a proved zero, avoiding a zero literal and subtraction.
  - dispatch-compare-chain: candidate; Lowers high-level command dispatch automatically; small proven dispatches may use indirect or super-dark dispatch.

Machine Features Used:
  - indirect-flow: Optimizer selected register-held branch addresses for one-cell indirect flow.; К БП/К ПП/К x?0 indirect flow commands are available to the optimizer.
  - error-stops: Compiler emitted a domain-error pause or explicit trap.; Domain-error stops are available only when the source semantics permits trap-like termination.
  - code-data-overlay: Layout marked address cells as reusable code/data overlay candidates.; Address operands, constants, opcodes, and display bytes may share cells after conflict checks.
  - address-constants: Layout marked address cells as reusable constants.; Address cells may double as constants for indirect flow and data transforms.

Proofs:
  - return-stack-empty: proved; No ПП opcodes were emitted; empty return stack precondition holds for В/О-as-БП01 rewrites.
  - indirect-addressing-ranges: proved; Indirect selectors are rewritten only after local data-flow proves a stable target, a compiler-owned address preload, or the fractional R0 sentinel shape.
  - value-ranges: proved; Collected source ranges for clue.
  - observability: proved; Visible state is limited by display output: clue.

Rejected Candidates:
  - display __inline_show_39_0/packed-storage-reuse: 999999 steps; display fields are not proved to already occupy their decimal positions
  - display __inline_show_39_0/packed-display-helper: 2 steps; display is not repeated often enough for a shared packed display helper
  - display __inline_show_39_0/display-byte-helper: 999999 steps; display is not repeated often enough for a shared display-byte helper
  - display __inline_show_39_0/display-byte-builder: 999999 steps; display has no literal/X2-sensitive fragments to build

Cell Roles:
  04: 06 address, constant, overlay - address can be reused as constant; code/data overlay allowed"
