  - display __inline_show_32_0/packed-display-helper: 2 steps; display is not repeated often enough for a shared packed display helper
  - display __inline_show_32_0/display-byte-helper: 999999 steps; display is not repeated often enough for a shared display-byte helper
  - display __inline_show_32_0/display-byte-builder: 999999 steps; display has no literal/X2-sensitive fragments to build
  - if@52/negative-zero-threshold-flow: 10 steps; Negative-zero threshold flow estimated at 10 cells; ordinary condition was shorter (6).

